  "Description": {
    "English": "A highly-advanced upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Pulse Engine</span>, vastly increasing <span class=\"name name-stellar\">fuel efficiency</span>.<br><br>Tritium supplies are redirected into a cycle of miniature black holes. Resulting micro-gravity fluctuations are harnessed to boost starship propulsion beyond conventional combustion-based approaches.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">脉冲驱动器</span>的一种极为先进的升级组件，能够大幅提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃料效率</span>。<br><br>氚的供给物料会直接导入微缩黑洞的循环。所引发的微重力波动会被用于提升飞船的推动力，能量大小超越常规燃烧方法所产生的动力。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">脈衝引擎</span>的極致先進升級項目，能大幅提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃料效率</span>。<br><br>氚補給會重新導向迷你黑洞的循環，形成的微重力波動能用來加速太空船推進力，遠超出傳統的燃燒引擎更強。"
  },
